Making the death penalty sting I can agree with. It makes you afraid to die. I disagree about corpse runs though. I don't think it adds to the community. There are a lot of other things that can add to the community in better ways. Corpse runs are just a waste of time and not something that I want in VSoH. If I have a set time to log off because of RL things like getting up in the morning, the last thing I want to do is die 15 minutes before that and spend another two hours online trying to get my corpse back. Leaving the corpse until the next day would suck because then I would need to spend a lot of time trying to get people to help. <br />
<br />
Corpse runs do nothing but make the game frustrating.
                  
